    "is_free": false,
    "description": "踏入《辉石纪：远征》，你将踏足一场2D像素风的史诗冒险。世界被来自未知之处的“黑雾”笼罩，但这并非是逐渐消散的噩梦，相反，“黑雾”的高度却在不断上升。<br><br>人们只能聚集于高山之巅，躲避“黑雾”的侵袭。然而，“黑雾”并非不可抗拒，神秘的“辉石”能够驱散黑雾，维持并扩大人类仅有的生存空间。<br><br>在这场远征中，你将引领主角与一支冒险队，穿越黑雾笼罩的土地，寻找有限的“辉石”或揭示“黑雾”的真相。然而，随着时间的推移，黑雾的高度不断攀升，使得寻找“辉石”的任务变得愈发紧迫。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特点</strong></h2><br><strong>1. 丰富独特的Boss战体验</strong><br>在Demo版本中，就有6场引人入胜的Boss战，整个游戏将提供更多充足场次的Boss战，确保你体验到淋漓尽致的战斗乐趣。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/8910158ccb639350c0377002c9bcaab0.poster.avif?t=1715700720\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/8910158ccb639350c0377002c9bcaab0.webm?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/8910158ccb639350c0377002c9bcaab0.mp4?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/685166e9ec6884d0756013106a7877e7.poster.avif?t=1715700720\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/685166e9ec6884d0756013106a7877e7.webm?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/685166e9ec6884d0756013106a7877e7.mp4?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>2. 多样化的怪物种类</strong><br>游戏中分布着数十种不同类型的怪物，避免了通过疯狂增加怪物数量或血量来强行提高游戏难度。每一场遭遇都将是独一无二的挑战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/2ad8cf2289b243b11d267051ea112b0a.poster.avif?t=1715700720\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/2ad8cf2289b243b11d267051ea112b0a.webm?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/2ad8cf2289b243b11d267051ea112b0a.mp4?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>3. 神秘奥术法术系统</strong><br>法术效果取决于施法时所装备的不同属性能量的奥术结晶。解锁各种神秘法术，体验战斗中的无尽可能性。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/4ba2ab515818e15e1d4a547d53ca7663.poster.avif?t=1715700720\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/4ba2ab515818e15e1d4a547d53ca7663.webm?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/4ba2ab515818e15e1d4a547d53ca7663.mp4?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>4. 多样化的装备组合</strong><br>数十种装备，每一件都拥有独特效果。通过巧妙的搭配，你可以探索不同的地区或击败不同的Boss。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/208b14b54aa07552c7d0e4641e5edfaa.poster.avif?t=1715700720\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/208b14b54aa07552c7d0e4641e5edfaa.webm?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/208b14b54aa07552c7d0e4641e5edfaa.mp4?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>5. 完整、细致且世界观衬托的剧情任务</strong><br>游戏包含多条支线剧情和小任务，通过各种NPC和精心设计的剧情，呈现出游戏丰富的背景故事。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/c0e47e0db5ce41eed558c0817a2c398f.poster.avif?t=1715700720\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/c0e47e0db5ce41eed558c0817a2c398f.webm?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/c0e47e0db5ce41eed558c0817a2c398f.mp4?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>6. 和谐精致的像素风2D画面</strong><br>尽管游戏使用了来自各个素材商店的素材，但开发者努力使画风看起来和谐统一。游戏提供了一个视觉上愉悦而一致的像素风画面。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/c49bc4c517fd5d1807dc03f73b8241d9.poster.avif?t=1715700720\" width=480 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/c49bc4c517fd5d1807dc03f73b8241d9.webm?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375410/extras/c49bc4c517fd5d1807dc03f73b8241d9.mp4?t=1715700720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>*因为本游戏仅有一人开发，如果遇到任何Bug或者翻译等方面错误，欢迎通过各种渠道来反馈！<br>*有因为精力确实有限，部分语言的翻译工作还在进行中，尽情期待~",
